'''Lorenzo''', '''Nikolas''', '''Myrinda''' and '''Zachary Brino''' (born September 21, 1998, in Woodland Hills, California) are the quadruplets born to Tony and Shawna Brino. They have an older half-brother, their father's son from another marriage, named Antonio, who is in the [[U.S. Coast Guard Academy]].
